{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>An unchanging, deceptive full moon looms over Tokyo, </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>where peaceful nights are now lost to the zombies...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HIGH-SPEED SURVIVAL ACTION WITH JUST 2 BUTTONS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/twmactiongif.gif?t=1732546860\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Simple Controls, Thrilling Combat</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stand your ground and slash zombies attacking from both sides!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master the game with just two buttons, or play comfortably with mouse clicks, keyboard, or gamepad</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chain your attacks to increase damage and score - but beware, enemies will speed up too! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/twmpugif.gif?t=1732546860\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unlock &amp; Power Up</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Power up your character with collected coins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your fighting style with 15 different upgrades, including 3 devastating flame techniques</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge yourself with high scores and time attack modes! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/hibanachan_gif_moto.gif?t=1732546860\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Since the unchanging, deceptive full moon began to rise, this city has lost its peaceful nights. In the zombie-infested streets of nighttime Tokyo, where people wander under the moon's spell, &quot;Hibana&quot; stands her